<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fluvial processes rather than fire primarily disturb stands. Plants sprout vigorously from the trunk and root crown when top-killed by fire.</div>
